casebody.data:
Jerryl L. Keane v. John D. Cucurello et al. Jerryl L. Keane, pro se, on the motion. Jerryl L. Keane, pro se, on the amendment. Submitted December 3

decided December 3, 1969

Submitted December 2 decided December 3, 1969

The motion by the plaintiff for a reruling on her request for a transcript in the appeal from the Superior Court in Fairfield County is denied.

The request by the plaintiff entitled “Amendment to the Plaintiff’s Motion for Re-Ruling on Transcript and Motion to Re-Argue the Defendant’s Motion to Deny the Appeal” is denied.
